name: Free Soul
description:
This is a fractal art design based on generative algorithms resulting from an exploration process when shapes, atmosphera, lights and colors are combined to create an unique and expressive representation of our feelings.  

Fractal art is a form of algorithmic art created by calculating fractal objects and representing the calculation results as still digital images, animations and media. The mathematical beauty of fractals lies at the intersection of generative art and computer art.
